des: Zombie No zombie is a fun turn-based voice game of discovery to let you know who's really sitting on your couch. Or if you're wonder if that zombie-bunny bite is transforming you - play one on one. You may not have a magic mirror mirror on a wall, but you and your friends do have Alexa Alexa to see your goofy inner reflections.
